"{\"uid\": \"thehindubusinessline.com-brandhub-students-represented-south-india-chefs-association-won-gold-medals-at-ika-culinary-olympics-2024-in-germany-article67903204.ece\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"+\\u00a0447.05  +\\u00a0152.70  +\\u00a047.00  +\\u00a01,732.00  +\\u00a04,170.00  +\\u00a0447.05  +\\u00a0152.70  +\\u00a0152.70  +\\u00a047.00  +\\u00a047.00  +\\u00a01,732.00  Get businessline apps on  Connect with us  TO ENJOY ADDITIONAL BENEFITS  Connect With Us  Get BusinessLine apps on  The IKA / International Culinary Olympics 2024 medal winners are posing with the South India Chef Association (SICA) board members.Sitting (L-R):Chef Mr. Sheetaraman Prasad N, General Secretary, SICA   Mr. R. Boominathan, Chairman, Chennais Amirta International Institute of Hotel Management       Chef Dr. Dhamodharan K, President, SICAStanding (L-R):Chef Mr. Elango Rajendran, Advisory Council, SICA   Chef Mr. Jugesh Arora, Honorary President, SICA   Chef Mr. Karthick, Trainer   Winner Chef Jagan S   Winner Chef Sreya Aneesh   Winner Chef Ankith K Shetty   Winner Chef Punith J   Winner Chef M A Akash George    Chef Mr. Sendhil\\u00a0Kumar,\\u00a0Trainer.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 878, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 233, \"end\": 236, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Industrias_Kaiser_Argentina\", \"score\": 0.9999991627113426, \"rank\": 7.823066397050752e-07, \"text\": \"IKA\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Industrias_Kaiser_Argentina\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Industrias_Kaiser_Argentina\"}, {\"begin\": 253, \"end\": 270, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Exhibition_of_Culinary_Art\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Culinary Olympics\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Exhibition_of_Culinary_Art\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Exhibition_of_Culinary_Art\"}, {\"begin\": 310, \"end\": 321, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/India\", \"score\": 0.6601587534741409, \"rank\": 0.5108902894836964, \"text\": \"South India\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/India\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/India\"}, {\"begin\": 597, \"end\": 606, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rajendran\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Rajendran\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rajendran\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rajendran\"}, {\"begin\": 649, \"end\": 654, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Arora\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.718865648433422e-16, \"text\": \"Arora\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Arora\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Arora\"}, {\"begin\": 692, \"end\": 700, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kartikeya\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Karthick\", \"types\": [\"Q24229398\", \"Q178885\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kartikeya\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kartikeya\"}, {\"begin\": 863, \"end\": 868, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nitish_Kumar\", \"score\": 0.4946887827738944, \"rank\": 0.5630261296751121, \"text\": \"Kumar\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nitish_Kumar\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nitish_Kumar\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Students from Chennais Amirta International Institute of Hotel Management representing South India Chef's Association, a premier body for culinary professionals from the finest hotels, restaurants and culinary institutions in South India, created history by bringing home India's first prestigious gold medals at IKA / Culinary Olympics 2024, the world's most prestigious culinary event, held in Germany recently.\", \"from\": 880, \"to\": 1293, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1152, \"end\": 1157, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/India\", \"score\": 0.9999982455521532, \"rank\": 1.4773564853605824e-06, \"text\": \"India\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/India\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/India\"}, {\"begin\": 1276, \"end\": 1283, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Germany\", \"score\": 0.9922577047719149, \"rank\": 0.0071383402630312365, \"text\": \"Germany\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Germany\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Germany\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Students bagged as many as ten medals, including three gold and six silver, and students took part in the competitions under various categories.\", \"from\": 1294, \"to\": 1438, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"IKA/Culinary Olympics is organised once in every four years.\", \"from\": 1440, \"to\": 1500, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1440, \"end\": 1443, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Industrias_Kaiser_Argentina\", \"score\": 0.9999991627113426, \"rank\": 7.823066397050752e-07, \"text\": \"IKA\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Industrias_Kaiser_Argentina\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Industrias_Kaiser_Argentina\"}, {\"begin\": 1444, \"end\": 1461, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Exhibition_of_Culinary_Art\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Culinary Olympics\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Exhibition_of_Culinary_Art\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Exhibition_of_Culinary_Art\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Its beginnings dating back to 1900, the Olympics is the oldest - as well as the largest and most diverse, international culinary arts competition in the world.\", \"from\": 1501, \"to\": 1660, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"However, no Indian had won a gold medal in these 124 years.\", \"from\": 1661, \"to\": 1720, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1673, \"end\": 1679, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indian_people\", \"score\": 0.999999854699137, \"rank\": 1.2988771669746404e-07, \"text\": \"Indian\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indian_people\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indian_people\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The students ended India's long drought for medals in this global event were: Chef Sreya Aneesh, who won 1 gold and 2 silver medals; Chef Jagan S and Chef Punith J who won 1 gold and 1 silver medal each; Chef Ankith K Shetty who won 2 silver medals, and Chef M A Akash George who won 1 bronze medal.\", \"from\": 1721, \"to\": 2020, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1740, \"end\": 1745, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/India\", \"score\": 0.9999982455521532, \"rank\": 1.4773564853605824e-06, \"text\": \"India\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/India\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/India\"}, {\"begin\": 1859, \"end\": 1864, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cheddi_Jagan\", \"score\": 0.999742184966432, \"rank\": 0.0002578815191666912, \"text\": \"Jagan\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cheddi_Jagan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cheddi_Jagan\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Chef Sreya Aneesh won in the categories of displaying and in live carving of fruits and vegetables, and others secured the medals in the live carving category.\", \"from\": 2021, \"to\": 2180, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The students were from the Bengaluru and Chennai campuses of Chennais Amirta International Institute of Hotel Management.\", \"from\": 2182, \"to\": 2303, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2209, \"end\": 2218, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bangalore\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.0533545889372275e-17, \"text\": \"Bengaluru\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bangalore\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bangalore\"}, {\"begin\": 2223, \"end\": 2230, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chennai\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.752470213266413e-19, \"text\": \"Chennai\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chennai\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chennai\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"They competed among 2000 chefs/participants from 67 countries.\", \"from\": 2304, \"to\": 2366, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The participants received the guidance of SICA trainers, and Chennais Amirta's faculty team comprising Chef Karthick, and Chef Senthil Kumar.\", \"from\": 2367, \"to\": 2508, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2475, \"end\": 2483, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kartikeya\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Karthick\", \"types\": [\"Q24229398\", \"Q178885\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kartikeya\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kartikeya\"}, {\"begin\": 2494, \"end\": 2501, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Senthil\", \"score\": 0.9876071807154763, \"rank\": 0.012548328451569573, \"text\": \"Senthil\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Senthil\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Senthil\"}, {\"begin\": 2502, \"end\": 2507, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nitish_Kumar\", \"score\": 0.4946887827738944, \"rank\": 0.5630261296751121, \"text\": \"Kumar\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nitish_Kumar\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nitish_Kumar\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Congratulating the medal winners,Chef Dr. Damu, President andChef Mr. Seetharam Prasad, General Secretary, SICA said, \\\"The gold medals are coming our way for the first time in the past 124 years.\", \"from\": 2510, \"to\": 2705, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2617, \"end\": 2621, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Central_American_Integration_System\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"SICA\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Central_American_Integration_System\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Central_American_Integration_System\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We are happy for the students who achieved this historic milestone.\", \"from\": 2706, \"to\": 2773, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"We thank them for representing SICA.\", \"from\": 2774, \"to\": 2810, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"This is just a beginning.\", \"from\": 2811, \"to\": 2836, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Chennais Amirta students achievement will inspire all the students and professionals in India's culinary sector to participate and win medals in the Olympics.\", \"from\": 2837, \"to\": 2995, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2925, \"end\": 2930, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/India\", \"score\": 0.9999982455521532, \"rank\": 1.4773564853605824e-06, \"text\": \"India\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/India\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/India\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We would also like to thank our SICA trainers & Chennais Amirta faculties, whose guidance and support proved to be invaluable for the students.\\\"\", \"from\": 2996, \"to\": 3140, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"In his comments,Mr.\", \"from\": 3142, \"to\": 3161, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Boomee Naathan,Chairman, Chennais Amirta International Institute of Hotel Management, said, \\\"I am extremely happy that our students have made this greatest accomplishment in the global arena, shining a spotlight on India's culinary prowess.\", \"from\": 3162, \"to\": 3402, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3377, \"end\": 3382, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/India\", \"score\": 0.9999982455521532, \"rank\": 1.4773564853605824e-06, \"text\": \"India\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/India\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/India\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This triumph will undoubtedly pave the way for more successes in the future and will inspire countless young talents.\", \"from\": 3403, \"to\": 3520, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I extend immense gratitude to SICA & Chennais Amirta faculties for entrusting our students with this prestigious opportunity.\\\"\", \"from\": 3521, \"to\": 3647, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3551, \"end\": 3555, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Central_American_Integration_System\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"SICA\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Central_American_Integration_System\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Central_American_Integration_System\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Website:https://chennaisamirta.com/  \\\"This is a company press release that is not part of editorial content.\", \"from\": 3649, \"to\": 3757, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"No journalist of The Hindu was involved in the publication of this release.\\\"\", \"from\": 3758, \"to\": 3834, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3775, \"end\": 3784, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Hindu\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.061152812518189e-39, \"text\": \"The Hindu\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q234460\", \"Q11032\", \"Q1092563\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Hindu\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Hindu\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Published on  March 1, 2024  Copyright\\u00a9 2025, THG PUBLISHING PVT LTD. or its affiliated companies.\", \"from\": 3836, \"to\": 3934, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"All rights reserved.\", \"from\": 3935, \"to\": 3955, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"BACK TO TOP  Comments have to be in English, and in full sentences.\", \"from\": 3957, \"to\": 4024, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"They cannot be abusive or personal.\", \"from\": 4025, \"to\": 4060, \"e